title: The 20YA | A Lifetime of Memories
body_text: 20 years ago today - two full decades - my life drastically changed.. and improved. I've said countless times that I'm absolutely the luckiest and most fortunate through it all - what a magnificent journey, even beyond the courts. See you on September 27 🙂 (my birthday!)
